@HostAddress = http://localhost:5032

### Process Payment
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/payments/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "amount": 199.99,
  "method": "CreditCard"
}

###

### Refund Payment
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/payments/refund
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "amount": 199.99
}

###

### Get Payment Status
@paymentId = 3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/payments/{{paymentId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Validate Payment Method
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/payments/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "method": "CreditCard",
  "cardNumber": "1234-5678-9012-3456"
}

